description: This operation returns a list of a specified search job.

parameters.name: SearchJobIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique string that specifies the search job.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The next item following a partial list of returned search job results. For example, if a request is made to return MaxResults number of search job results, NextToken allows you to return more items in your list starting at the location pointed to by the next token.

nested_items.name: Results
nested_items.description: The results consist of either EBSResultItem or S3ResultItem.

nested_items.name: S3ResultItem
nested_items.description: These are items returned in the search results of an Amazon S3 search.

nested_items.name: BackupResourceArn
nested_items.description: These are items in the returned results that match recovery point Amazon Resource Names (ARN) input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: SourceResourceArn
nested_items.description: These are items in the returned results that match source Amazon Resource Names (ARN) input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: BackupVaultName
nested_items.description: The name of the backup vault.

nested_items.name: ObjectKey
nested_items.description: This is one or more items returned in the results of a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata that match the values input for object key.

nested_items.name: ObjectSize
nested_items.description: These are items in the returned results that match values for object size(s) input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the returned results that match values for item creation time input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: ETag
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the returned results that match values for ETags input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: VersionId
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the returned results that match values for version IDs input during a search of Amazon S3 backup metadata.

nested_items.name: EBSResultItem
nested_items.description: These are items returned in the search results of an Amazon EBS search.

nested_items.name: BackupResourceArn
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of recovery points returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: SourceResourceArn
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of source resources returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: BackupVaultName
nested_items.description: The name of the backup vault.

nested_items.name: FileSystemIdentifier
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for file systems returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: FilePath
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for file paths returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: FileSize
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for file sizes returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for creation times returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTime
nested_items.description: These are one or more items in the results that match values for Last Modified Time returned in a search of Amazon EBS backup metadata.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The next item following a partial list of search job results.
